tc_game_scripts.script_contents:
import clr from System.IO import File, Path clr.AddReference("TCAdmin.SDK") from TCAdmin.SDK.Misc import CompressionTools
# Delete file if it already exists if File.Exists(FileNameSavePath+'.zip'): File.Delete(FileNameSavePath+'.zip')
if File.Exists(FileNameSavePath): try: # File is compressed as a zip when downloaded, but isn't a zip file. Rename to .zip, extract and delete file. File.Move(FileNameSavePath, FileNameSavePath+'.zip') mapsFolder = Path.Combine(ThisService.RootDirectory, 'csgo', 'maps') c=CompressionTools() c.ThrowException = True c.Decompress(FileNameSavePath+'.zip', mapsFolder) File.Delete(FileNameSavePath+'.zip') except IOError, e: raise Exception("Failed to extract %s, error was:\n%s" % ('csgo/maps/' + FileNameNoPath, e))
